Expose small POSIX compatibility surfaces needed by upstream Git.

Git's process runner is patched to use the existing AgentOS posix_spawn
broker on WASI, but some linked translation units still reference standard
headers and functions such as syslog, paths, exec, alarm, network lookup,
and interval timers. Expose those declarations in the owned sysroot and
provide runtime shims in libc-bottom-half overrides.

